/greenlang/cli/pack.py @greenlang/security
/.github/workflows/security*.yml @greenlang/security
/.github/workflows/policy-gate.yml @greenlang/security

# Documentation team reviews all docs
/docs/ @greenlang/docs
*.md @greenlang/docs
/examples/ @greenlang/docs

# DevOps/Platform team reviews infrastructure
/.github/workflows/ @greenlang/platform
/Dockerfile @greenlang/platform
/docker-compose*.yml @greenlang/platform
