/helm/ @greenlang/platform
/scripts/ @greenlang/platform

# Data team reviews connectors and datasets
/greenlang/connectors/ @greenlang/data
/greenlang/datasets/ @greenlang/data

# Core team reviews critical components
/greenlang/core/ @greenlang/core
/greenlang/orchestrator/ @greenlang/core
